OL,3,CTribute to 'dearly loved' teenager who
OL,4,Cdied in crash just after 18th birthday
OL,6,FThe family of a teenager who died in a
OL,7,Fcrash near Wareham just after his
OL,8,Feighteenth birthday have said he was
OL,9,F'dearly loved'.
OL,11,FJoshua Blake was a passenger in a
OL,12,Fblack Volvo V70 which was involved in
OL,13,Fa single-vehicle collision on Morden
OL,14,FRoad on the evening of Wednesday 18
OL,15,FFebruary.
OL,17,FOfficers received a report of the
OL,18,Fincident at 8.42pm and Joshua was
OL,19,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
