OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772547085
OL,3,CTribute to 'dearly loved' teenager who
OL,4,Cdied in crash just after 18th birthday
OL,6,FOfficers are continuing to support his
OL,7,Ffamily.
OL,9,FThe driver of the vehicle ` a man in
OL,10,Fhis 20s ` and another male teenage
OL,11,Fpassenger suffered serious injuries
OL,12,Fand remain in hospital.
OL,14,FIn a tribute, Joshua's family said:
OL,15,F"Joshua had only just celebrated his
OL,16,F18th birthday before he tragically
OL,17,Flost his life.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
