PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772547085
OL,3,CTribute to 'dearly loved' teenager who
OL,4,Cdied in crash just after 18th birthday
OL,6,F"He leaves behind his loving parents
OL,7,FMartin and Caroline, brother Samuel,
OL,8,Fsister Chloe, his wider family and
OL,9,Fmany friends.
OL,11,F"Joshua had a passion for supercars,
OL,12,Fwhich he always took the opportunity
OL,13,Fto photograph. He enjoyed riding his
OL,14,Fmotorbike.
OL,16,F"He was dearly loved and will be
OL,17,Fgreatly missed, always remembered by
OL,18,Fall who knew him."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@RO]
